wLText.wltc: FAQ

accordionItems.accTitle: How do interior designers charge for their professional  design time ?
accordionItems.accContent:
Hiring an interior designer is an investment in saving you time and acquiring the peace of mind that your job is being executed professionally, in a cost-effective manner and to your liking.

Currently, there is no one industry standard for how interior designers bill for their professional time, but there are three common formats - Hourly, Flat Fee and Cost Plus.
